{"tid":549674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終於有外國人明粵語同普通話嘅分别","createTime":"2018-02-04T00:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T03:37:19.000Z","uid":142503,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7282300e596e55a4fd68abc2c33a47edc4ac3161","tid":549674,"uid":142503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T00:42:53.000Z","msg":"頭先喺YouTube揾到呢條片<br />\n都係最近先出嘅片嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n裏面啲嘢錯咗少少 外國人做嘅片預咗<br />\n但So far已經好足夠同啲外國人解釋粵語<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s2km_z4-1T8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs2km_z4-1T8&d=tYzvHa%2B5RX6vNR4h1n2%2FEQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5140a655\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s2km_z4-1T8</a><br />\n<br />\n大家如果係喺其他國家嘅話 不妨畀啲外國朋友睇下條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">支持粵語 撐粵語入文</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286b63e32103b69e554de31f2ff2106d95d82a52","tid":549674,"uid":142503,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話識廣東話冇乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到普通話全世界都用噉 又咩有競爭力<br />\n其實以前大陸未定呢個官方語言前撚有人識咩 咪又係北方啲人先識<br />\n普通話嘅文化影響力咪又係有努力推廣先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真 大家都應該努力推廣呢個語言 唔好步廣州後塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一可以做嘅就係<br />\n學粵拼 確保自己讀音正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n粵語入文 確保自己唔打5P字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0ce47058d50d3bce9ba9a0532042f5c256b909","tid":549674,"uid":142503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55370180f53af6cdf8aa7f5e5c9ffee679a5fdca","tid":549674,"uid":11695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41be67d74c5c0f87b4410d708c9051538b99999e","tid":549674,"uid":12158,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"鬼佬就算撐粵又點？香港人都會笑人普通話講得唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係齊心撐粵就應該褒揚古天樂啦當年。古仔喺前線打仗，班友喺後欄恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1322254ba74d75a94eb80f6388a057a54384fc","tid":549674,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb94d3c9516f84bb0b5578092ce93adf58f5b30","tid":549674,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:22:48.000Z","msg":"打左5p字刀冇人吊拉，同連登仔講粵語入文笑死唔笑死"},{"pid":"35c1ef89d21ba725b0e32b0d6ed5be50016353e6","tid":549674,"uid":142503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41be67d74c5c0f87b4410d708c9051538b99999e","tid":549674,"uid":12158,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"鬼佬就算撐粵又點？香港人都會笑人普通話講得唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係齊心撐粵就應該褒揚古天樂啦當年。古仔喺前線打仗，班友喺後欄恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:30:44.000Z","msg":"香港人啲普通話差就畢狃㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(題外話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人話不嬲嘅正字係畢狃 我唔肯定但照用住先)<br />\n<br />\nBTW 我有個同學係廣州人 我哋啲香港人都會笑佢啲口音奇怪或者讀音唔準<br />\n硬係覺得佢哋係因為冇一套有系統嘅方法學廣東話 只靠口耳相傳 先會搞到啲發音完全亂嚟 大概啱就算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9824ab5e0bf45a872323ac383e16b0661d270d72","tid":549674,"uid":142503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35c1ef89d21ba725b0e32b0d6ed5be50016353e6","tid":549674,"uid":142503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41be67d74c5c0f87b4410d708c9051538b99999e","tid":549674,"uid":12158,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"鬼佬就算撐粵又點？香港人都會笑人普通話講得唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係齊心撐粵就應該褒揚古天樂啦當年。古仔喺前線打仗，班友喺後欄恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:30:44.000Z","msg":"香港人啲普通話差就畢狃㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(題外話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人話不嬲嘅正字係畢狃 我唔肯定但照用住先)<br />\n<br />\nBTW 我有個同學係廣州人 我哋啲香港人都會笑佢啲口音奇怪或者讀音唔準<br />\n硬係覺得佢哋係因為冇一套有系統嘅方法學廣東話 只靠口耳相傳 先會搞到啲發音完全亂嚟 大概啱就算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"唔記得講重有唐人街啲華僑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明以前都曾經係香港人<br />\n之前有個啊姐重話自己以前住寶琳定點<br />\n結果講出嚟啲廣東話完全唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先令我深深感受到 唔推廣粵拼 只靠口頭上咁學 遲早實玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全香港遲早個個譚仔口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692ebca7195bab14fd2fdd81c92330269b7ac1ca","tid":549674,"uid":15428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2676487ab927174499bc47782d8072cbf8acb25","tid":549674,"uid":142503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T02:11:27.000Z","msg":"大家唔好畀呢個PO停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f64c3156b0c04232a24464e8718589bdab6106