語廣府片先係粤語代表。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"係嘅 小弟見識少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都略知粵語有唔同分支<br />\n<br />\n純粹係見到個廣州同學好多懶音 唔會捉正嚟講噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先會覺得佢哋冇真真正正咁學<br />\n<br />\n無意冒犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}